html.body: Purine nucleosides can be synthesize in two ways, de novo biosynthesis and salvaging pathways. In salvaging pathways nucleosides from RNA and DNA breakdown can reenter purine nucleoside de novo biosynthesis. Website=www.biocyc.org/Ecoli/Pathways/ free text=Voet and Voet (textbook) Biochemistry
